        public static java.util.HashMap<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> manageValueElectroencephalography(byte[] value)
        Transform method for electroencephalography sensor. The data comes into a dictionary, the keys of this dictionary are consecutive number (0, 1, 2, etc) regarding to each returned value.
        Explanation for dictionary values:

        • 0 => Attention value (%)

        • 1 => Meditation value (%)

        • 2 => Poor signal quality value (%)

        • 3 => Low alpha signal value (mV)

        • 4 => High alpha signal value (mV)

        • 5 => Low beta signal value (mV)

        • 6 => High beta signal value (mV)

        • 7 => Low gamma signal value (mV)
